 href=\"message/\">トップメッセージ</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"work\"><a href=\"work/\">人と仕事</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"project\"><a href=\"project/\">プロジェクトストーリー</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"voice\"><a href=\"voice/\">ボイス</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"recruit\"><a href=\"recruit/\">採用情報</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</nav>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"site-header__trigger\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>\r\n\t\t</header>\r\n\t\t<section class=\"scroll-point-section\" id=\"intro\">\r\n\t\t\t<div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<h2><strong>Recruitment 2027</strong><br>Penta-Ocean Construction Co., Ltd.<br>Recruitment information for students graduating in 2027</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t<p>The <strong>CORE</strong> of <em>Spirits</em></p>\r\n\t\t\t\t<p>There are many kinds of works varying from a norm or standard. If you are going to bother to do it, you might as well do a work which you can have a spirit of challenge on. What is the matter, even if you had no idea on your work, couldn’t make it perfect, or whatever failures you’ve encountered at the beginning? The most important thing is whether or not you can keep strong motivation, positive behavior and put in loads of effort toward your work. People regarded it as a “Dream” or “Determination”. If you keep on having a “Dream” or “Determination”, you will be appropriately understood and rewarded by the people around you, and be able to influence people and move the company to achieve its goal, as well as to accomplish the works which are meaningful, fun and meeting the needs of the society. Someday, we believe that your enormous experience maturity will give you a core position in our company to lead Penta-Ocean to revolve around the world.</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t<audio controls loop autoplay>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<source src=\"media/audio/snd_bgm_01.ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<source src=\"media/audio/snd_bgm_01.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t\t</audio>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"#news\" class=\"assist type-b\"></a>\r\n\t\t</section>\r\n\t\t<section class=\"scroll-point-section\" id=\"news\">\r\n\t\t\t<div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<h3>News & Information</h3>\r\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><time datetime=\"2026.04.01\">2026.04.01</time><a href=\"https://axol.jp/zw/s/penta-ocean_28/mypage/login\" target=\"_blank\">2026年度インターンシップのエントリー受付を開始しました。</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><time datetime=\"2026.04.01\">2026.04.01</time><a href=\"https://www.penta-ocean.co.jp/recruit/internship/\" target=\"_blank\">インターンシップ特設サイトをオープンしました！</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><time datetime=\"2026.03.01\">2026.03.01</time><a href=\"https://job.axol.jp/bx/s/penta-ocean_27/mypage/\" target=\"_blank\">2027年度新卒採用エントリー受付を開始しました。</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</section>\r\n\t\t<section class=\"scroll-point-section\" id=\"core\" class=\"compact\">\r\n\t\t\t<h2>The CORE</h2>\r\n\t\t\t<div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<p>「創造する心に国境はない」<br>この信念のもと、国内外で数多くの建設工事を担っている五洋建設。<br>その発祥は明治時代に遡ります。</p>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"core/vision.html\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thumbnail\"><img src=\"media/images/core/index/thm_vision_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3>CORE 01 \"Vision\"</h3>\r\n\t\t\t\t</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"core/honesty.html\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thumbnail\"><img src=\"media/images/core/index/thm_honesty_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3>CORE 02 \"Honesty\"</h3>\r\n\t\t\t\t</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"core/future.html\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thumbnail\"><img src=\"media/images/core/index/thm_future_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"image\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3>CORE 03 \"Future\"</h3>\r\n\t\t\t\t</a></li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"maximage\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"media/images/core/index/img_visual_01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</section>\r\n\t\t<section class=\"scroll-point-section\" id=\"index\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"core/\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thumbnail\"><img src=\"med